{"title":"New Santa Cruz Hightower v4 29er Blurs Lines with 150mm Travel Jump & Better VPP","link":"https://bikerumor.com/my25-santa-cruz-hightower-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-updated-with-150mm-travel/","date":1726556460000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_big-mountain-rides-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"2024 Santa Cruz Hightower longer travel 150mm new VPP carbon 29er all-mountain bike, creek crossing\" /></p>\n<p>This new 4th-generation evolution of the Santa Cruz Hightower is more capable than ever, shifting the 29er all-mountain bike a little further towards enduro, and blurring lines between disciplines a bit further. Just like the recent Bronson overhaul, the new 4th-generation Santa Cruz Hightower gets a completely reshaped VPP for a burlier ride, plus a longer travel boost, too! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sure, it might now be harder than ever to pick between the Bronson and this new Hightower. But 29er fans will be pretty psyched to get a more capable all-mountain bike!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2024 Santa Cruz Hightower carbon 29er all-mountain bike updates</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Santa Cruz Hightower longer travel 150mm new VPP carbon 29er all-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-297x165.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike-768x427.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Santa Cruz)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you loved the updates to the latest playful do-it-all-mountain <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2024-santa-cruz-bronson-carbon-all-mountain-bike-updated/\" target=\"_blank\">Bronson gen 5</a>, but still feel like you really need big 29″ wheels for a faster enduro-tastic ride, this gen4 Santa Cruz Hightower is going to be right up your alley. Now, the Hightower gets the same 150mm rear wheel &amp; 160mm fork travel as the Bronson. And it’s really just the wheel sizes that set the two bikes apart.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Santa Cruz Hightower longer travel 150mm new VPP carbon 29er all-mountain bike, blur\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-jpg.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_life-is-a-blur-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Slacker geometry than before and a lower-slung and more efficient VPP suspension design, this is the one bike to rule them all for wagon wheel fanatics. Think of it as a shorter-travel, more realistic Megatower… the solution for mountain bikers looking for the “mythical do-it-all bike”.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2024 Santa Cruz Hightower longer travel 150mm new VPP carbon 29er all-mountain bike, angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-jpg.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_angled-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The real big shift here is from the 145/150mm travel of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-santa-cruz-hightower/\" target=\"_blank\">gen3 29er Hightower</a> to 150mm out back &amp; 160mm up front for the Santa Cruz Hightower gen4, still with 29″ wheels. 5mm more at the rear wheel, 10mm more at the front wheel. More travel simply means more capability on the steepest and most technical trails. This is a fast-rolling bike meant to fly over all sorts of terrain. And more travel means more fun- whether on all-day adventure rides or trips to the bikepark.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-jpg.webp\" alt=\"MY25 Santa Cruz Hightower 150mm VPP carbon all-mountain bike,  lower VPP layout\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_revised-VPP-layout-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, exactly like on the Bronson, Santa Cruz reconfigured the Hightower’s long-running VPP (virtual pivot point) suspension layout. By moving the key lower link forward and the main pivot slightly down, Santa Cruz say they’ve lowered the bike’s anti-squat. The result is a more supple bike that can soak up the big bumps even when you are standing on the pedals and filter out trail chatter even when you are pedaling. There’s also a side benefit that the new bike is approved for coil shocks too, with more room to fit everything low in the frame.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-jpg.webp\" alt=\"MY25 Santa Cruz Hightower 150mm VPP carbon all-mountain bike,  lower anti-squat\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_Anti-squat-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Santa Cruz call it all-around better VPP performance for a better all-rounder bike…”<em>Reduced pedal kickback on square-edge hits. Remains active while pedaling up and across rough, technical terrain. Less anti-squat benefits descending sensitivity due to the reduced pedal kickback associated with standing on the pedals.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>New 29er All-mountain geometry</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-jpg.webp\" alt=\"MY25 Santa Cruz Hightower 150mm VPP carbon all-mountain bike, updated geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY2025-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-4_longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_updated-geometry-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With longer travel, the new Hightower also gets slacker geometry at around a 64° headtube angle – depending on flip-chip position. The change is relatively small – just 0.6° slacker than the previous generation – but it pairs to almost 2° steeper seattubes and slightly longer (+5mm) frame Reach to shift weight forward for more control going up and down.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new bike also gets slightly longer chainstays – again sticking with size-specific rear center dimensions to provide a consistent balanced ride feel to mountain bikers of all sizes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-jpg.webp\" alt=\"MY25 Santa Cruz Hightower 150mm VPP carbon all-mountain bike, frameset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MY25-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-150mm-VPP-carbon-all-mountain-bike_CC-Factory-Float-X-frameset_Matte-Deep-Purple-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>5 sizes (S-XXL) with proportional geometry</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Glovebox secure internal frame storage in the downtube under the bottle cage mount</li>\n\n\n\n<li>enclosed fully-guided internal cable routing from the sides of the headtube</li>\n\n\n\n<li>C carbon frames are compatible with mechanical shifting</li>\n\n\n\n<li>now CC carbon frames only include internal routing for a rear brake &amp; dropper post – wireless electronic shift-only</li>\n\n\n\n<li>2.5″ max tire clearance, front &amp; rear</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Boost 148mm spacing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Post Mount brakes with 200mm front /180mm rear rotors</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ISCG05 chain guide mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>BSA Threaded bottom bracket</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Santa Cruz UDH</li>\n\n\n\n<li>IS 1.5″ tapered headset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lifetime frame warranty</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easy-to-source, easy-to-service bearings</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_non-driveside-detail-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_non-driveside-detail-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"2024 Santa Cruz Hightower longer travel 150mm new VPP carbon 29er all-mountain bike, new VPP layout\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_non-driveside-detail-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_non-driveside-detail-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-carbon-29er-all-mountain-bike_non-driveside-detail-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024-Santa-Cruz-Hightower-longer-travel-150mm-new-VPP-ca